title: [Gyldemar Forest, Ancient Road]
description: Bits of bricks and mortar lie scattered across the ground to form a rough road.  A line of maorals line the road, their branches arching to form a canopy for the rubble.

Bits of bricks and mortar lie scattered across the ground to form a rough road.  A line of maorals line the road, their branches arching to form a canopy for the rubble, further darkening the area in the night.
